--The International Olympic Committee said that they will award the Olympic Order to balloonists Bertrand Piccard and Brian Jones who are the first to circumnavigate the world in a balloon.
--A Swiss-Belgian team took off from a lake-side mountain in the Swiss Alps in the latest bid to balloon non-stop around the world.
